#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:159
msgid "Adding an E2EE device"
msgstr "新增 E2EE 裝置"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:166
msgid "Setup a new desktop client"
msgstr "設定新的桌面客戶端"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:180
msgid "Setup a new Android device"
msgstr "設定新的 Android 裝置"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:194
msgid "Setup a new iOS device"
msgstr "設定新的 iOS 裝置"

#: ../../files/using_e2ee.rst:208
msgid ""
"In the browser, first enable E2EE in the personal settings. This is needed, "
"as E2EE is less secure in the browser, requiring you to fully trust the "
"administrator to not alter the source code the browser will execute. E2EE "
"folders are currently read-only. Therefore, it is not possible to add, "
"remove, edit, or share an E2EE file from the browser."
msgstr ""
"在瀏覽器中，需先於個人設定啟用 E2EE。這是因為 E2EE 在瀏覽器環境中的安全性較低，需完全信任系統管理員不會修改瀏覽器所執行的原始碼。目前 "
"E2EE 資料夾僅支援唯讀，因此無法在瀏覽器中新增、刪除、編輯或分享 E2EE 檔案。"

